# Request an export and read the resulting artifact. In PR6 the export job is a
# skeleton: it validates the request, resolves the duration policy, and records
# a `pending_render` artifact. Real MP4 rendering is deferred to PR5.

### Create an export job
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/projects/proj_local/timelines/tl_current/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: export-final-001

{
  "format": "mp4",
  "quality": "standard",
  "audioAssetIds": ["asset_narration"],
  "durationPolicy": "match_longest_media"
}

# 201 Created
# {
#   "job": {
#     "id": "job_export_1",
#     "type": "export",
#     "status": "succeeded",
#     "projectId": "proj_local",
#     "result": { "artifactId": "art_99ff00aa" }
#   }
# }

### Poll the export job
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/projects/proj_local/exports/job_export_1

### Read the artifact
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/projects/proj_local/artifacts/art_99ff00aa

# 200 OK
# {
#   "artifact": {
#     "id": "art_99ff00aa",
#     "projectId": "proj_local",
#     "kind": "video/mp4",
#     "status": "pending_render",
#     "url": null,
#     "timelineId": "tl_current",
#     "durationSec": 60,
#     "renderPlan": {
#       "durationPolicy": "match_longest_media",
#       "durationSec": 60,
#       "timelineDurationSec": 58,
#       "audioDurationSec": 60,
#       "audioAssetIds": ["asset_narration"],
#       "format": "mp4",
#       "quality": "standard"
#     }
#   }
# }

### Mismatch example — fail_on_mismatch returns a typed 422 error
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/projects/proj_local/timelines/tl_current/exports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "audioAssetIds": ["asset_narration"],
  "durationPolicy": "fail_on_mismatch",
  "maxDeltaSec": 1.0
}

# 422 Unprocessable Entity
# {
#   "error": {
#     "code": "audio_timeline_mismatch",
#     "message": "Audio and timeline durations differ beyond the allowed threshold.",
#     "requestId": "req_…",
#     "details": { "timelineDurationSec": 58, "audioDurationSec": 72, "deltaSec": 14, "maxDeltaSec": 1 }
#   }
# }
